devdoc.details: Simple leaderboard contract for Banana Fever Dream game Stores all scores for each player address with basic validation Only accepts scores from players who have paid via CoinSlot contract

getAllScores().details: Get all scores (for off-chain sorting and display)

returns._originalWallets: Array of corresponding original wallet addresses
returns._scores: Array of all scores for this player

getTotalScores().details: Get total number of score entries

returns._0: Total number of score entries submitted

setCoinSlotAddress(address).details: Set or update the CoinSlot contract address

params._coinSlotAddress: Address of the CoinSlot contract Only owner can call this function

submitScore(uint256,address).details: Submit a score to the leaderboard

params._originalWallet: The original wallet address (EOA) Requirements: - Score must be greater than 0 - Original wallet address must not be zero address - Original wallet must have paid via CoinSlot contract Note: msg.sender can be smart account, but _originalWallet must have paid

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfer ownership to a new address
